rem kiosk
rem 8/17/2017

do Examine Kiosk Machine
 [
  ifflag have mission
   [
    print The kiosk machine sits at the front of the entrance. Customers use it to
    print convert new yen into arcade credits.
   |
    print The kiosk machine sits at the front of the entrance. Customers use it to
    print convert new yen into arcade credits. Your contact from the Black Net stands
    print next to it watching you carefully.
   ]
 ]

do Use Kiosk Machine
 [
  ifflag have mission
   [
    print You'd have to log your C.I.N. in order to use it, and you're a better criminal
    print than that.
   |
    print Your contact is standing next to it. You better just give him the signal.
    setflag signal
   ]
 ]

ifflag have mission
 [|
  ifflag signal
   [
    do Signal Contact
     [
      print When he glances your way, you shake your right hand holding three fingers out.
      print
      print He nods, then waves you over.
      go Contact
     ]
   |]
 ]
